---
By: Tauler
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 196
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - God's Will
---
He who serves God after God’s will shall be rewarded accordingly to his own
will; but he who prays to God according to his own will shall not be answered
in accordance with his own will, but after God’s will.
